About Tejasvi Pal
Hey there! I'm Tejasvi (pronounced Tej-asvee), a Machine Learning & Infrastructure Engineer

When I’m not fine-tuning models or optimizing infrastructure, I’m probably levelling up my
workout routine, experimenting with high-protein vegetarian meals, or mapping out my next big
journey.
